cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL. 

The paper proposes a method for reducing computation cost in deep neural networks for computer vision tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves training-based computation-cost-reduction, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves optimization of computations, which can be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves experiments on image classification datasets, which can be categorized under cs.CL (Computation and Language).
